      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of exceptional pedigree, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This unit remains in showroom condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Every mechanical system has been meticulously vetted to ensure peak performance, offering a driving experience that is indistinguishable from its initial delivery. For the collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class.",
