      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior, has been meticulously maintained to satisfy the most discerning buyer. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of unrivaled aesthetic integrity and mechanical excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
